# API测试示例
# 使用VS Code的REST Client插件或Postman执行

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = your_admin_token_here

### 1. 获取房源审核列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/room-review/list?current=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 提交房源审核
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/room-review/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "reviewComments": "房源信息完整，照片清晰，位置优越",
  "reviewCriteria": {
    "location": 9,
    "facilities": 8,
    "photos": 9,
    "description": 8,
    "pricing": 8
  }
}

### 3. 获取房源审核详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/room-review/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. 获取直接入住申请列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/direct-move-in/list?current=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. 处理直接入住申请
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/direct-move-in/process/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "processNotes": "申请理由充分，同意直接入住"
}

### 6. 获取直接入住申请详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/direct-move-in/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. 获取房东权限列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/landlord-permission/list?current=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. 更新房东权限
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/landlord-permission/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "canPublishRooms": true,
  "canManageReviews": false,
  "canHandleApplications": true,
  "permissionLevel": "LIMITED",
  "expiresAt": "2025-12-31T23:59:59"
}

### 9. 授予房东权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/landlord-permission/grant
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "landlordId": 2,
  "canPublishRooms": true,
  "canManageReviews": true,
  "canHandleApplications": true,
  "permissionLevel": "FULL",
  "expiresAt": "2025-12-31T23:59:59"
}

### 10. 测试错误情况 - 无效的房间ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/room-review/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 99999,
  "reviewComments": "测试无效房间ID",
  "reviewCriteria": {
    "location": 5,
    "facilities": 5,
    "photos": 5,
    "description": 5,
    "pricing": 5
  }
}

### 11. 测试权限验证 - 无token访问
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/room-review/list
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. 批量查询测试
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/room-review/list?reviewStatus=PENDING&publisherType=LANDLORD
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json